        "subject": "LU-18939 tests: add missing run_test for test_854",
        "message": "LU-18939 tests: add missing run_test for test_854\n\nThe commit be4e323b56 added test_854 to verify\nreadahead parameters can be set as percentage, but\nforgot to add the run_test command to actually\nexecute the test.\n\nThis patch adds the missing run_test 854 command.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial testlist=sanity env=ONLY=854\nFixes: be4e323b56 (\"LU-18939 llite: allow readahead params to be set as percentage\")\nChange-Id: Ifc59853d6b085939bc52e16eaac3b0b2dbbdbc97\nSigned-off-by: Patrick Farrell <pfarrell@whamcloud.com>\n"
